[center]This is a conversion of the Tera Castanic Heavy 15 for UUNP with HDT

REQUIREMENTS: 
You will need an original fashion by Halo can download it [url=http://mod.dysintropi.me/mods/Skyrim/UNPCMTERACastanicHeavy15Black.7z]here[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36213/?]HDT HighHeels System[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53996/?]HDT Physics Extensions[/url], by Hydrogen
HDT physics compatible skeleton(Groovtama's [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26800/?]XPMS Extended[/url] recommended)
The latest [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49015/?]Bodyslide[/url]

A standalone black version of the tier 11 Castanic Heavy armour from the MMORPG TERA. Requires HDT High Heels.

who don't know UUNP is bodyslide for unp so you can make your own custom bodies based off any unp body you wantYou can have the original unp or you can use unp if you want. You can use any 7b body and there is much more.It works the same way that it does for CBBE and it is included in bodyslideSo all you have to do is download that and this mod and build it in bodyslide and it will change to the body you chose

Thanks:
Caliente for Bodyslide
